@prefix : <http://antroporama.iolanta.tech/> .
@prefix media: <http://antroporama.iolanta.tech/media/> .

@prefix rdf: <https://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
